elling of   Louis  , or a pet form of   Lewis ."]},{"name":"Louie","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Lewie   or   Louis  , currently in fashion."]},{"name":"Lewi","meanings":["form, since the Middle Ages, of the French name   Louis .  In modern use it is also in part a transferred use of the surname derived from this given name, or from Anglicized forms of Gaelic <i>Mac Lughaidh</i> ‘son of  <b>Lughaidh</b> ’  or Welsh Llewelyn ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Louis de Bours de Bournonville was born in 1102, in Bours, Hautes-Pyrénées, Midi-Pyrénées, France, his father, Robert de Bours, was 23 and his mother, Berthe de Bournonville, was 19. He married Jehanne de Rollancourt in 1124. They were the parents of at least 2 sons and 1 daughter. He died in 1154, in his hometown, at the age of 52."},"et":{"1102–1154":"1102–1154","–Male":"Surnud","1107–1159":"1107–1159","1124–1178":"1124–1178","1125–1187":"1125–1187","1128–1179":"1128–1179","1079–1124":"1079–1124","1083–1132":"1083–1132","1132":"1132","1154":"1154","1187":"1187","1083":"1083","1107":"1107","1128":"1128","1159":"1159","1125":"1125","1102":"1102","1124":"1124","1179":"1179","1079":"1079","1178":"1178","1100":"1100","Bours, Pas-Calés, Heuts-d'Franche, Française":"Bours, Hautes-Pyrénées, Midi-Pyrénées, Prantsusmaa","Bours, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France":"Bours, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Bours, Arras, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France":"Bours, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1102–1154":"1102–1154","–Male":"Kuollut","1107–1159":"1107–1159","1124–1178":"1124–1178","1125–1187":"1125–1187","1128–1179":"1128–1179","1079–1124":"1079–1124","1083–1132":"1083–1132","1132":"1132","1154":"1154","1187":"1187","1083":"1083","1107":"1107","1128":"1128","1159":"1159","1125":"1125","1102":"1102","1124":"1124","1179":"1179","1079":"1079","1178":"1178","1100":"1100","Bours, Pas-Calés, Heuts-d'Franche, Française":"Bours, Hautes-Pyrénées, Midi-Pyrénées, Ranska","Bours, Pas-de-Calais,